'''康平學堂'''（'''Campion Hall'''）是[[牛津大學|牛津大學]]的一個[[永久私人學堂|永久私人學堂]]，由英國的[[耶穌會|耶穌會]]管理。學堂建築由[[埃德溫·魯琴斯|埃德溫·魯琴斯]]設計。

==歷史==

1896年9月9日，[[牛津大學聖約翰學院|牛津大學聖約翰學院]]的校友理查德·克拉克（Fr. Richard Clarke）遵照他在倫敦[[农场街教堂|农场街教堂]]的上級人士的指令，來牛津開辦一所為信仰耶穌會的牛津本科生提供教育的學堂，即今康平學堂的前身克拉克堂（Clarke's Hall）。最初學堂位于牛津聖吉爾斯街（St Giles'）40號，克拉克為首任院長。1896年9月10日迎來第一個學生<ref>The Reckoned Expense: Edmund Campion And The Early English Jesuit, page ix, Woodbridge 1996</ref><ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite web|url=http://archive.catholicherald.co.uk/article/1st-october-1971/4/on-the-other-side-the-statutes-of-the-university-o|title=Catholic Herald|accessdate=2016-09-30|archive-date=2013-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927080506/http://archive.catholicherald.co.uk/article/1st-october-1971/4/on-the-other-side-the-statutes-of-the-university-o|dead-url=no}}Retrieved on 20 January 2013</ref>。因爲原先租下的40號太小，所以在15個月後學院又搬到了11號，一直待到1936年爲止<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.headington.org.uk/oxon/stgiles/tour/east/11.htm|title=Headington.co.org|accessdate=2016-09-30|archive-date=2012-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120928002824/http://www.headington.org.uk/oxon/stgiles/tour/east/11.htm|dead-url=no}} Retrieved on 20 January 2013</ref>。1918年該大學獲得永久私人學堂的地位，並改現名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://jesuitinstitute.org/Conferences/VenueCampionHall.htm|title=Jesuitinstitute|access-date=2016-09-30|archive-date=2020-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201162642/http://jesuitinstitute.org/Conferences/VenueCampionHall.htm|dead-url=no}}Retrieved on 20 January 2013.</ref>。

到1933年達西（Fr. D'Arcy）擔任院長的時候，學堂與聖吉爾斯街11號業主簽定的合同差3年就要到期了<ref>The Fordham Ram, Fr.d'Arcy Assumes University Post, page.1, New York, 20 October 1939, No.5</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://archive.catholicherald.co.uk/article/1st-october-1971/4/on-the-other-side-the-statutes-of-the-university-o|title=Catholicherald|accessdate=2013-02-02|archive-date=2013-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927080506/http://archive.catholicherald.co.uk/article/1st-october-1971/4/on-the-other-side-the-statutes-of-the-university-o|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在放棄了于聖吉爾斯街再建一所新房子的計劃之後，學堂在布魯爾街（Brewer Street）建起了新家<ref name="british-history.ac.uk">{{cite web|url=http://www.british-history.ac.uk/report.aspx?compid=63896|title=British History Online|access-date=2016-09-30|archive-date=2014-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140818224625/http://www.british-history.ac.uk/report.aspx?compid=63896|dead-url=no}} Retrieved on 20 January 2013</ref>。新建築由[[埃德溫·魯琴斯|埃德溫·魯琴斯]]設計，在1936年完工，1954年成爲[[登錄建築|登錄建築]]（等級為II*）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://list.english-heritage.org.uk/resultsingle.aspx?uid=1046738 |title=Campion Hall (including chapel) |work=The National Heritage List for England |publisher=[[English_Heritage|English Heritage]] |accessdate=20 September 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060814/http://list.english-heritage.org.uk/resultsingle.aspx?uid=1046738 |archive-date=2013-09-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。除去[[汤姆方庭|汤姆方庭]]的一個噴泉不算，這是魯琴斯为牛津设计的唯一一所建築<ref>{{cite book |title=Lutyens: The Work of the English Architect Sir Edwin Lutyens (1869–1944) |chapter=Catalogue of Works by Sir Edwin Lutyens |last=Richardson |first=Margaret |year=1981 |publisher=[[Arts_Council_of_Great_Britain|Arts Council of Great Britain]] |location=London |isbn=0-7287-0304-1 |page=196}}</ref>，風格則為科茨沃爾德式<ref name=Amery>{{cite book |title=Lutyens: The Work of the English Architect Sir Edwin Lutyens (1869–1944) |chapter=Campion Hall, Brewer Street |last=Amery |first=Colin |year=1981 |publisher=[[Arts_Council_of_Great_Britain|Arts Council of Great Britain]] |location=London |isbn=0-7287-0304-1 |page=146}}</ref>。

